        <title>使用 Snipaste 截出圆角矩形带阴影的截图</title>
        <link>https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/p/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-snipaste-%E6%88%AA%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%86%E8%A7%92%E7%9F%A9%E5%BD%A2%E5%B8%A6%E9%98%B4%E5%BD%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE/</link>
